{"tid":2143555,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支持政府「止暴制亂」的31歲髮型師向同事揮刀 判處160小時社會服務令","createTime":"2020-08-07T07:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T10:48:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"454cc9fac67f40867c0b27d729b2cdab47c01697","tid":2143555,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:14:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">被告張展明</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/08/20200807_CR_%E5%BC%B5%E5%B1%95%E6%98%8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F08%2F20200807_CR_%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%2598%258E.jpg&h=754682ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年2月1日，髮型師因政見不合扯掉同事一束頭髮，並以刀恐嚇同事，早前承認普通襲擊及管有攻擊性武器兩罪，今在九龍城法院判刑。嚴舜儀主任裁判官接納感化官建議，兩項控罪分別判處160小時社會服務令，同期執行。<br />\n<br />\n31歲被告張展明被控於今年2月1日在尖沙咀一間髮廊襲擊男子黃漢德，以及管有攻擊性武器，即一把長30厘米的刀。<br />\n<br />\n案情指出，被告和事主是共事的髮型師，二人因政見不合爭執，雙方糾纏，期間被告扯脫事主一束頭髮，再衝入茶水間拿出放有廚刀的紙盒，並打開盒蓋以刀恐嚇事主，隨即被在場其他人士喝止，其後被捕。被告在警誡下表示「我同佢糾纏先至扯佢頭髮，同埋我拎把刀出嚟係想嚇啫，唔係想斬佢」，承認當時自己失控，強調並沒有從紙盒拿出廚刀。"},{"pid":"a3476cecb532a07587d4fd15782d0552ddd4d97f","tid":2143555,"uid":522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"藍絲 = 低智商低EQ"},{"pid":"eb0268554e7ba9cf67afd522548def449d1cdbaf","tid":2143555,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3476cecb532a07587d4fd15782d0552ddd4d97f","tid":2143555,"uid":522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"藍絲 = 低智商低EQ"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj